howmanybaked<-1000 #1
breadmean<-950     #
breadsd<-20        #
days<-10000         #

1

bakedbreads<-rnorm(howmanybaked, mean=breadmean, sd=breadsd)
hist(bakedbreads,breaks=seq(850,1100,1), main="")

boughtr<-NULL
for(i in 1:days){
  bakedbreads<-rnorm(howmanybaked, mean=breadmean, sd=breadsd)
  boughtr<-c(boughtr,sample(bakedbreads,1))
}
hist(boughtr,breaks=seq(850,1100,1), main="")
